---
title: NexusDB - System Context Diagram (C4 Level 1)
---

graph TB
    subgraph External["External Systems"]
        Developer["👤 Developer<br/>Writes NexusQL schemas & queries"]
        AIApp["🤖 AI Application<br/>RAG, Agents, LLM Apps"]
        MCPClient["🔧 MCP Client<br/>AI Agent Tool Discovery"]
    end

    subgraph NexusDB["NexusDB - Embedded Graph-Vector Database"]
        CLI["Nexus CLI<br/>nexus-cli"]
        Server["Nexus Server<br/>nexus-container"]
        Engine["Core Engine<br/>nexus-db"]
        Explorer["Nexus Explorer<br/>nexus-explorer"]
    end

    subgraph Storage["Storage Layer"]
        LMDB["LMDB<br/>Storage Engine"]
    end

    subgraph SDKs["Client SDKs"]
        TSSDK["TypeScript SDK<br/>nexus-ts"]
        PySDK["Python SDK<br/>nexus-py"]
    end

    Developer -->|nexus init/check/push| CLI
    CLI -->|deploys queries| Server
    CLI -->|compiles via| Engine

    AIApp -->|HTTP queries| TSSDK
    AIApp -->|HTTP queries| PySDK
    TSSDK -->|port 6969| Server
    PySDK -->|port 6969| Server

    Server -->|graph + vector ops| Engine
    Engine -->|ACID transactions| LMDB

    MCPClient -->|MCP protocol| Server
    Server -->|tool discovery| Engine

    Explorer -->|visual inspection| Server

    classDef external fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#666,stroke-width:2px
    classDef nexus fill:#7289da,stroke:#4a69bd,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef storage fill:#b8e6b8,stroke:#2d8f2d,stroke-width:2px
    classDef sdk fill:#f9d56e,stroke:#d4a017,stroke-width:2px

    class Developer,AIApp,MCPClient external
    class CLI,Server,Engine,Explorer nexus
    class LMDB storage
    class TSSDK,PySDK sdk
